SelfDisposable - class in io.scanbot.core
Wrapper for a native object to make it auto-finalizable after some time of the object being unusedThe need for this wrapper is came from the fact that the Native memory usage is not visible for GC, so for some classes like DC it stays in memory for some time even after the object is not actually used.
